ARM: dtsi: axp81x: set pinmux for GPIO0/1 when used as LDOs

On AXP813/818, GPIO0 and GPIO1 can be used as LDO as (respectively)
ldo_io0 and ldo_io1.

Let's add the pinctrl properties to the said regulators.

